{"tid":1556711,"cid":28,"subCid":0,"title":"有無可能做到pin message或局部edit一樓","createTime":"2019-09-10T00:08:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-12T02:31:29.000Z","uid":132447,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"bbc171322d15bdcd65c5a953fe1c2f56427af9a3","tid":1556711,"uid":132447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T00:08:08.000Z","msg":"好多時集中推緊post 人入黎只會睇一樓而miss左之後有用既討論<br />\n而且無得edit既時候更加無辦法將果d有用資訊整合補返俾人知，往往都係重新開post但就分薄左人氣<br />\n<br />\n所以有兩個諗法：<br />\n1. 可以俾樓主揀其中一個回覆pin左佢係每一頁頭show出黎，好似而家自害alert 咁，有新資料想加時候就可以出個新回覆pin左佢俾後入既人睇到<br />\n<br />\n2. 局部edit一樓，樓主可以edit一樓，但無得改打左既字，只可以加新字上去<br />\n<br />\n希望可以加是但一個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"756d5042c64ee65784f4e33fc8ee9579f26006da","tid":1556711,"uid":132447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T00:10:00.000Z","msg":"輕輕推"},{"pid":"2052426119998288843ea477082ca975065b922b","tid":1556711,"uid":132447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T18:00:30.000Z","msg":"輕輕推"},{"pid":"35d907d3d4b9730e16aeacaf28e897504bb0b4d9","tid":1556711,"uid":132447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T17:15:55.000Z","msg":"輕輕推"},{"pid":"7d93bbdfd2d6145fee21de46d65ecc876dc61382","tid":1556711,"uid":132447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T02:31:29.000Z","msg":"輕輕推"}]}